10. The surface mountable assembly of claim 1 further including:
a rotatable knob configured to selectively engage movement of the second assembly with respect to the first assembly;
a locking knob operable to selectively fix the first assembly with respect to the second assembly.

14. A surface mountable assembly for a light line generating device comprising:
a first assembly including a first side and a second side, wherein the first side engages a work surface;
a second assembly coupled to the second side of the first assembly; and
a laser diode assembly including a laser diode housing, wherein:
the second assembly is selectively translatable along the first assembly along a first direction to reposition the laser diode housing with respect to the work surface;
the laser diode housing is selectively rotatable along a second direction to adjust the location of the laser diode housing with respect to the work surface.
